## Scope

- Applies to **every user request related to code or features** in this repository **by default**.
- **Opt-out:** "skip workflow" / "kein Workflow", "quick fix" / "nur quick fix", "no merge" / "kein Merge", "nur Erklärung, kein Code", "suggestion only", "explore only" / "nur spike" / "read-only".
- If intent is ambiguous, ask **one concise message** with all open questions before deviating.

**Full playbook:** `.cursor/rules/smash-up-full-workflow-detail.mdc` (Phases 1–14, recovery, stack).

