## Unified gates (use `TodoWrite` on long runs; close items when done)

### Pre-code gate (**Full track only**)

Do **not** call `StrReplace`, `Write`, `Delete`, or implementation `Shell` until:

```
[ ] Phase 1 — Analyze: explore subagent launched and awaited; affected files/patterns known
[ ] Phase 2 — Ticket: docs/tickets/YYYY-MM-DD-short-slug.md (ticket-authoring.mdc)
[ ] Phase 3 — Plan: if matrix says Plan → SwitchMode(plan) + CreatePlan + user confirm; else skip with brief rationale
[ ] Phase 4 — Branch: from latest dev (see detail)
```

**Exploration → implementation:** Read-only/spike first is fine; switching to implementation **restarts** Full pre-code from Analyze as needed. **Inline markdown plans** are not a substitute for Plan mode when Plan is required.

### Pre-commit gate (all tracks that change code)

```
[ ] shell subagent (background) ran tests — awaited, green
    Local:    ddev exec php artisan test
    Cloud VM: php artisan test   (only when ddev describe confirms DDEV absent)
[ ] ReadLints on all touched files — clean
[ ] composer audit run — no unresolved critical/high CVEs
[ ] Migration rollback tested (migrate:rollback + migrate) — if migration included
[ ] .env.example updated — if new env vars introduced
[ ] lang:check clean — if any resources/lang/ file changed
[ ] Docs: README/docs/CHANGELOG per detail Phase 8
[ ] Roadmap: updated if Phase 1 scan matched — or valid Roadmap: N/A
[ ] Public copy: EN/DE lang + CHANGELOG if visitor-notable — or Public copy: N/A
```

**DDEV rule:** Always prefer `ddev exec php artisan …` / `ddev composer …` / `ddev npm …`. Bare commands only on confirmed Cloud VM (DDEV absent).

